  "detailed_description": "Tactic Boxing is a boxing game with ragdoll physics, local multiplayer, career mode and manager mode.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Active Ragdoll Physics<br />\r\n- 3 Boxing Styles: Puncher, Slugger, Out-Boxer<br />\r\n- 9 skills (strength, accuracy, health, stamina, footwork, attack speed, chin, HP and SP recovery)<br />\r\n- 40 boxers (not real)<br />\r\n- In-Game Editor<br />\r\n- Training Camp<br />\r\n- Game Settings (damage, health, knockout chance, etc.)<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Career Mode<br />\r\n- Manager Mode<br />\r\n- Quick Fight Mode<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Player vs AI<br />\r\n- AI vs AI<br />\r\n- Player vs Player (Local Multiplayer) (a controller is required for local multiplayer)<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Mouse and keyboard controls<br />\r\n- Gamepad controls",
  "about_the_game": "Tactic Boxing is a boxing game with ragdoll physics, local multiplayer, career mode and manager mode.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Active Ragdoll Physics<br />\r\n- 3 Boxing Styles: Puncher, Slugger, Out-Boxer<br />\r\n- 9 skills (strength, accuracy, health, stamina, footwork, attack speed, chin, HP and SP recovery)<br />\r\n- 40 boxers (not real)<br />\r\n- In-Game Editor<br />\r\n- Training Camp<br />\r\n- Game Settings (damage, health, knockout chance, etc.)<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Career Mode<br />\r\n- Manager Mode<br />\r\n- Quick Fight Mode<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Player vs AI<br />\r\n- AI vs AI<br />\r\n- Player vs Player (Local Multiplayer) (a controller is required for local multiplayer)<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Mouse and keyboard controls<br />\r\n- Gamepad controls",
